'''親愛的別哭'''（{{Lang-fr|La Guerre est déclarée}}）是2011年法國導演[[華蕾莉·董澤利|華蕾莉·董澤利]]的作品<ref>{{Cite book|title=International Film Guide 2012|url=https://archive.org/details/internationalfil0000unse_b7g9|last=Smith|first=Ian Hayden|accessdate=24 April 2012|year=2012|isbn=978-1908215017|page=[https://archive.org/details/internationalfil0000unse_b7g9/page/120 120]}}</ref><ref>[http://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=189699.html Index:La Guerre est déclarée] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allocine.fr/film/fichefilm_gen_cfilm=189699.html |date=20210507215743 }} www.allocine.fr.</ref>。該片代表法國參加2011年[[第84屆奧斯卡金像獎|第84屆奧斯卡]]的[[奥斯卡最佳外语片奖|最佳外语片奖]]<ref name="84th">{{Cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/france-makes-a-declaration-war-236454|title=France Makes a 'Declaration of War' in Foreign-Language Oscar Race|last=Leffler|first=Rebecca|date=16 September 2011|work=Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=2011-09-16}}</ref><ref name="AMPAS">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2011/20111013.html|title=63 Countries Vie for 2011 Foreign Language Film Oscar|accessdate=2011-10-14|work=oscars.org}}</ref>，但未入圍<ref name="Oscar Shortlist">{{Cite web|url=http://www.oscars.org/press/pressreleases/2012/20120118.html|title=9 Foreign Language Films Vie for Oscar|accessdate=2012-01-19}}</ref>。

